Today sucked. Found out I need my wisdom teeth out, and also found out I've lost my job for next year (because the...
body:
4 weeks

Today sucked. Found out I need my wisdom teeth out, and also found out I’ve lost my job for next year (because the place I was going to work has issues, I had nothing to do with it), and wedding planning has finally made me stressed AF.

Knowing in 4 weeks I get to see my idol? It makes me feel so much fkn better!

Thank you @taylorswift

Here we have my mum and I very excited with Taylor!! Finally met her!!1!1!1!1! AFTER TEN YEARS So excited because there’s only 40 days left until Rep Tour Brisbane!

(Snake Pit 1)

Hopefully one day these photos can become a reality ❤️

Taylor has been in my life for 10 years now and she’s basically family at this point, she’s shaped who I am and i can’t wait to see her again for the Reputation Tour, this tour is for us and i’m so ready for it ✨

summary: My dear! I am Gertrud! I've got tickets for the tour, airfare, and the hotel! I'm only waiting to meet you in November. It's...
body:
My dear! I am Gertrud!

I’ve got tickets for the tour, airfare, and the hotel!

I’m only waiting to meet you in November.

It’s been a lot of ups and downs, but it turned out to be good, and it was worth it.

Thank you for letting me know my best friend.

Hahahahaha speaking of, I recently encountered a relationship problem, I like a man who is 12 years older than me, it is very bad, but I can not stop completely, I now listen to Treacherous every day, it is my state of mind.

RED is really your best album.  I can feel the meaning of each song.

Thank you!

Today is also a day to love you!

@taylorswift

@taylornation
